To perform the subtask of clicking the shopping cart button, you can move the mouse to the shopping cart icon in the upper right corner of the page and click it. According to the screenshot provided, the shopping cart icon is located in the upper right corner of the screen.
The following is the JSON format for executing this action:```json
[
    {"action_type": "MouseAction", "mouse_action_type": "click", "mouse_button": "left", "mouse_position": {"width": 985, "height": 115}}
]
```
